          <para styleclass="Interface2"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Two Data-boxes </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">(for each Motion-Derivative) :</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="PopupTable2" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">End (</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">motion-value</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">) of Previous Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> (</text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" translate="true">Read-Only </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">or </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" translate="true">Read-Write</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">)</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">The data-box where you enter the motion-value for the End of the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Previous-Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">. </text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">E.g.: In the image above, the motion-value at the:</text></para>
                <para styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><image src="Red-14-1.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> &#160;</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">End of the Previous-Segment</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true"> = 40mm</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Start (</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">motion-value</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">) of the Selected-Segment </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">(</text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" translate="true">Read-Only</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> or </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" translate="true">Read-Write</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">)</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">The data-box where you enter the motion-value for the Start of the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Selected-Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">. </text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">E.g.: In the image above, the motion-value at the:</text></para>
                <para styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> &#160;</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Start of the Selected-Segment</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true"> = 60mm</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">These data-boxes have two possible states: </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Read-Only </text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">and </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Read-Write</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion-Law</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">, </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Motion-Derivative</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> and the </text><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Control-Buttons</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> determine the state of the two data-boxes.</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Three Control Buttons </text><image src="Red-14-3.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><image src="Red-14-4.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><image src="Red-14-5.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">(for each Motion-Derivative) :</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="PopupTable2" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="Red-14-3.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">End Control-Button</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">- controls if you can specify the motion-value for the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End of the Previous-Segment. </text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">It has three(3) possible states - </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Do Edit</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">, </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Do Not Edit</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">,</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Can Not Edit</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="Red-14-4.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Match Control-Button</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> - controls flow of motion-values from the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Previous-Segment</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> to the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Selected-Segment</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> . It </text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">has two(2) possible states - &#160;</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Do Force</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start of the Selected-Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> = &#160;</text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End of the Previous-Segment</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Do NOT Force</text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true"> Start of the Selected-Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> = &#160;</text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End of the Previous-Segment</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><image src="Red-14-5.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Start Control-Button</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true"> - </text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">control if you can specify the motion-value for the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-of the Selected-Segment. </text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">It has three(3) possible states - </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Do Edit</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">, </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Do Not Edit</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">,</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Can Not Edit</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">There are eight(8) different settings of the </text><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Three Control-Buttons</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">. </text><text styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">See </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Blend-PointEditor-ControlButtons" styleclass="SeeAlso" translate="true">Control Buttons: States and Patterns</link></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
